<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="hero">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:28px;">
        <div style="width:42px;height:42px;border-radius:12px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c85a2d,#9f3712);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;">
          <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="[URL]">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5" stroke="white" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <span style="font-family:'Newsreader',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:var(--ink);letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Adekunle<span style="color:var(--accent)">Agency</span></span>
      </div>
      <div class="eyebrow">Brcolumn_4/div>
      <h1>Tell us about your brand once. We handle the rest.</h1>
    </div>

    <form class="card" id="profileForm" enctype="multipart/form-data">
      <input type="hidden" name="source" value="brand_profile_form_v1">

      <!-- SECTION 1: Identity -->
      <div class="section">
        <h2>Brcolumn_5/h2>
        <p>What we need to identify and set up your brand correctly.</p>
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="brand_name">Brcolumn_6span style="color:var(--accent)">*</span></label>
            <input id="brand_name" name="brand_name" type="text" required placeholder="e.g. House of Tara">
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="brand_aliases">Other names column_7span class="opt">optional</span></label>
            <input id="brand_aliases" name="brand_aliases" type="text" placeholder="Comma-separated — e.g. HOT, Tara">
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="niche">Industry column_8span style="color:var(--accent)">*</span></label>
            <input id="niche" name="niche" type="text" required placeholder="e.g. Nigerian beauty, streetwear, food & beverage">
            <div class="hint">One short phrase is enough.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="brand_website">Brcolumn_9span class="opt">optional</span></label>
            <input id="brand_website" name="brand_website" type="url" placeholder="[URL]">
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="contact_email">Contact email <span style="color:var(--accent)">*</span></label>
            <input id="contact_email" name="contact_email" type="email" required placeholder="[EMAIL]">
          </div>
          <div class="field">
            <label for="contact_phone">WhatsApp / phone number <span class="opt">optional</span></label>
            <input id="contact_phone" name="contact_phone" type="tel" placeholder="e.g. 08012345678">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SECTION 2: Offer and Audience -->
      <div class="section">
        <h2>Offer column_10/h2>
        <p>The most important part. Be as specific as you can.</p>
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="field full">
            <label for="what_do_you_sell">What do you sell or offer? <span style="color:var(--accent)">*</span></label>
            <textarea id="what_do_you_sell" name="what_do_you_sell" required placeholder="Describe your product or service in a few sentences."></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="field full">
            <label for="target_customer">Who is your ideal customer? <span style="color:var(--accent)">*</span></label>
            <textarea id="target_customer" name="target_customer" required placeholder="e.g. Young working women in Lagos aged 22–35 who want premium but affordable beauty products."></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="field full">
            <label for="current_offer">Current offer, campaign, or seasonal focus <span class="opt">optional</span></label>
            <textarea id="current_offer" name="current_offer" placeholder="e.g. April promo on bridal packages, new sneaker drop, Ramadan offer, back-to-school bundle."></textarea>
            <div class="hint">Leave blank if no active campaign.</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

