      <div class="section">
        <h2>Voice and visual direction</h2>
        <p>Helps us match tone and style to your brand. Short answers are fine.</p>
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="field">
            <label for="tone_words">How should your brand sound? <span style="color:var(--accent)">*</span></label>
            <input id="tone_words" name="tone_words" type="text" required placeholder="e.g. bold, warm, aspirational">
            <div class="hint">3 to 5 words, comma-separated.</div>
